P(|Z|>t) \leq  \sqrt{\frac{2}{\pi}}\frac{e^ {\frac{-t^2}{2}}}{t} ~\forall t > 0
Z\sim \mathcal{N}(0,1)
t>0
P(|Z|>t)=P(Z^{-}<-t)+P(Z^{+}>t)
